{"tid":960486,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［你們的大哥］成 龍 最 新 專 輯 《我還是成龍》","createTime":"2018-12-29T12:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T14:52:06.000Z","uid":215823,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bcbae11d5d749074f80e12d4507dd848cf0f518c","tid":960486,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/29/204549_94b595bbc4508dc7d3ab04f97528d10e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F29%2F204549_94b595bbc4508dc7d3ab04f97528d10e.png&h=110c5c18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成龍最近推出新專輯《我還是成龍》接受新加坡傳媒專訪，當中每首歌都獻給不同的人，包括父母、妻子林鳳嬌、兒子房祖名、成家班兄弟等，其中房祖名就佔了3首歌。<br />\n成龍謂祖名於2014年吸毒被捕後，他心情相當複雜，雖然憤怒又心痛，但仍鼓勵兒子重新來過，<strong>還說美國大學沒有把祖名教好</strong>，就讓社會大學把他教好。他表示以前有請保鑣保護兒子，不過祖名後來寫了一首歌《人工牆》訴說想要自由，成龍就放手讓兒子自己成長，但一不管就出事，自認是做父親的失職。成龍用《路口》、《心痛》、《別放棄》3首歌唱出對兒子的愛，並直言現在的心態是，祖名喜歡做甚麼都可以，就是不能再犯同樣的錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n最後他這張專輯還寫了一首關於自己的「遺言」，唱出自己死後想講的說話，強調會喊死人：「我唱了一首我走了的歌，已經錄好了。我走了之後，我已經把整個唱片錄好，所有我的團隊勸我這首歌不能發，我說無所謂，我這個人是不迷信的，就是我想講的話先講，他們說大哥千萬不能發這首歌會哭死人的，我說好，但是我知道將來有一天，你們還當我是朋友的還當我是你們的大哥的，送喪的那一天哭死你們，這是我想做的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/29/204530_885e82caeb79d27e3fb7066f388173c3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F29%2F204530_885e82caeb79d27e3fb7066f388173c3.png&h=5566bb72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/29/204531_1fe2226a10e8931fd14be8151960ba3c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F29%2F204531_1fe2226a10e8931fd14be8151960ba3c.png&h=b8c43046&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f6eb3daec85fca49fa39a77031a53e53f1e4e20","tid":960486,"uid":167566,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"大哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854017ee5762683676dd7734133709726aa1aa1c","tid":960486,"uid":138658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7adde03f3aa615ab79112c1e51e364b8c8824073","tid":960486,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5721b1b2378ff6d77fdf0828d0d465aa50f4b7","tid":960486,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:51:06.000Z","msg":"咸左"},{"pid":"f08fb4a2ae15a69e8189869a4546e37756ed9962","tid":960486,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:52:41.000Z","msg":"咁快啲死比我喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075cb134f49fb58d71befd03c1c4a6af408aeb67","tid":960486,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"成龍 <br />\n<br />\n致全世界的影迷(獨白)<br />\n<br />\n作詞：成龍<br />\n作曲：成龍<br />\n編曲：成龍<br />\n<br />\n當年，這本書的名字一公佈，很多朋友都說，'大哥，這個書名說的就是你。'後來，我不斷收到很多認識的、不認識的朋友發來的資訊，跟我分享他們讀完這些故事的感受，我很開心。在寫這本書的時候，我只有一個原則，就是真誠，我希望讀者看到一個真實的我。<br />\n一路走來，我知道很多人喜歡我，也有很多人討厭我。有時候，看到那些斷章取義的報導，我的同事、朋友們會很生氣，他們會來跟我說，明明事實不是這樣，為什麼他們要這麼寫？大哥你為什麼不解釋？<br />\n我會跟大家說，真的不用每一次都去解釋。如果我真的做錯了，解釋也沒用。如果我沒有做錯，又何必去解釋？<br />\n其實，我也是慢慢才看開的，因為經歷的風浪太多太多了。就算做不到完美，我起碼努力做到真實，做到問心無愧，這就夠了。<br />\n再說，已經有這麼多人喜歡我，承受一些誤解和偏見，又算什麼呢？<br />\n唉，放心吧，有你們的陪伴，我永遠不老。"},{"pid":"200e183624ec47010b40238b870c2d973f4dbe90","tid":960486,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/29/205635_50e24bd8e74ae809d3d0afbd1a65c4dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F29%2F205635_50e24bd8e74ae809d3d0afbd1a65c4dc.png&h=a97f8f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過對於祖名犯錯，成龍竟然暗指唔關阿仔事：「是美國大學沒有把他教好！記得當時我沒有打過一次電話，乜沒看過他，甚麼都沒有，他根本不知我怎麼想。到他看見這些歌詞，才知原來我從沒放棄他。」"},{"pid":"11b30a31d7b686a6250c52e200f0b09a0871c39c","tid":960486,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T12:57:01.000Z","msg":"咸了"},{"pid":"4689289ad75ebdb7e7980636f92040f0fbaa425e","tid":960486,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"三姓家奴"},{"pid":"fa629489407c12e150195e1acd1b16820bdd8e21","tid":960486,"uid":228894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:12:29.000Z","msg":"DIU...擺起一副慈父樣.....<br />\n我想嘔....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9897bece988cc7059054bf957d2835330543f88a","tid":960486,"uid":163291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"鱷魚淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a9b803b9712f728708695d40027eb73c55ab6d","tid":960486,"uid":215823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9897bece988cc7059054bf957d2835330543f88a","tid":960486,"uid":163291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"鱷魚淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:31:07.000Z","msg":"唔捨得見到大哥咸"},{"pid":"07757bb34f8b95a0759c4380e7d7a4c26b65897d","tid":960486,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:33:32.000Z","msg":"大gor<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 甜咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d36665292249dae3e1e62107e3be39b9986029e","tid":960486,"uid":215823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/29/221618_9d6b031f13c782578d0c1cd6666965d8.p